ch.ethz.mxquery.datamodel.types
Class TypeInfo

java.lang.Object
  ch.ethz.mxquery.datamodel.types.TypeInfo

public class TypeInfo
extends java.lang.Object

Some of node kind types (e.g. element, attribute, PI) might have name part in the type definition. It's not possible to represent type with integer number in these cases.
